```yaml
- hosts: your_ec2_instance
  gather_facts: yes

    - name: Get EC2 instance tag

        name: your_ec2_instance
        region: us-west-2
        filters:
          instance-id: i-your_ec2_instance_id
      register: ec2_tag

    - name: Set template based on EC2 tag
      set_fact:
        config_template: config.j2
      when: ec2_tag.tags['YourTag'] == 'your_tag_value'

    - name: Include the selected template

        src: "{{ config_template }}"
        dest: /path/to/your/config/file
```
